---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import whatDoWeDo from '../../assets/what-do-we-do.jpg';
---

<section
id='what-do-we-do'
class='w-full bg-white dark:bg-gray-900'
>
<div class='max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row'>
<div
class='w-full md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center items-center px-6 py-12 sm:px-10 sm:py-16 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100'
>
<div class='max-w-md w-full'>
<h2
class='text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-6 sm:mb-8 font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white'
>
What do we do?
</h2>
<p class='mb-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 leading-relaxed'>
At our core we provide consultancy services for digital deliveries. This
can take the form of helping with executive and stakeholder management,
product leadership and team building, all the way to defining platforms
and helping to build and deploy them.
</p>
<p class='mb-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 leading-relaxed'>
We are always looking for ways to improve processes, deliver value
for-money solutions architecture and help with hands-on development.
</p>
<p class='mb-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 leading-relaxed'>
We have a broad range of technical and strategic skills to help startups
and corporates alike achieve the best solution for their businesses.
</p>
<p class='text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 leading-relaxed'>
Our goal is to provide value at every point for our clients and their
projects.
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class='w-full h-64 md:h-auto md:w-1/2'>
<Image
src={whatDoWeDo}
alt='Team collaborating on digital delivery solutions'
class='w-full h-full object-cover object-center'
loading='lazy'
/>
</div>
</div>
</section>